def learn(inputs: Array[String], output: String) {
    val env = senv
    val data = ImplicitDataToRatingParser.parseAll(env, inputs, ",", 1, 2, 0, startTimestamp)
    
    val factorModel = PSOfflineMatrixFactorization.psOfflineMF(
      data,
      numFactors = numFactors,
      learningRate = 0.05,
      iterations = iterations,
      rangeMax = factorRangeMax,
      iterationWaitTime = iterationWaitTime,
      rangeMin = factorRangeMin,
      negativeSampleRate = 19,
      pullLimit = pullLimit,
      workerParallelism = workerParallelism,
      psParallelism = psParallelism,
      userMemory = userMemoryLimit)
      
    factorModel.addSink(new VectorModelToFileSink(output))
    
    env execute s"generating model $output from $inputs"

}

def learnOnline(prevModel: String, inputs: String, nextModel: String) {
    val data = ImplicitDataToRatingParser.parse(senv, inputs, ",", 1, 2, 0, startTimestamp)
    
    val parsedModel = VectorModelFileParser.parseWithoutLength(senv, prevModel, numFactors)
        
    
    val newModel = PSOnlineMatrixFactorizationWithModelLoad.psOnlineMF(
        data,
        parsedModel,
        numFactors = numFactors,
        learningRate = 0.2,
        minRange = -0.1,
        maxRange = 0.1,
        negativeSampleRate = 19,
        pullLimit = 1600,
        workerParallelism = workerParallelism,
        psParallelism = psParallelism,
        iterationWaitTime = 10000)
        
    newModel.addSink(new VectorModelToFileSink(nextModel))
    
    senv execute s"Generating model $nextModel online"
}

def evaluate(input: String, model: String, output: String) {
    
    val env = senv
    val ratings = ImplicitDataToRatingParser.parse(env, input, ",", 1, 2, 0, startTimestamp)
    val parsedModel = VectorModelFileParser.parse(env, model, numFactors)
    
    val topK = PSOnlineLearnerAndTopKGeneratorWithModelLoad.psOnlineLearnerAndGeneratorWithModelLoad(parsedModel)(
        ratings, 
        numFactors = numFactors,
        rangeMin = factorRangeMin,
        rangeMax = factorRangeMax,
        learningRate = 0.7,
        negativeSampleRate = 99,
        userMemory = 65536,
        K = k,
        workerK = workerK,
        bucketSize = bucketSize,
        pruningAlgorithm = pruningAlgorithm,
        workerParallelism = workerParallelism,
        pullLimit = 500,
        psParallelism = psParallelism,
        iterationWaitTime = iterationWaitTime)
        
    nDCGSink.nDCGPeriodsToCsv(topK, output, 86400)
    
    env execute s"Online evaluation of model $model with learning"
}

def evaluateWithoutLearning(input: String, model: String, output: String) {
    
    val env = senv
    val ratings = ImplicitDataToRatingParser.parse(env, input, ",", 1, 2, 0, startTimestamp)
    val parsedModel = VectorModelFileParser.parse(env, model, numFactors)
    
    val topK = PSTopKGeneratorWithLEMP.psTopKGenerator(
        ratings, 
        parsedModel,
        rangeMin = factorRangeMin,
        rangeMax = factorRangeMax,
        numFactors = numFactors,
        workerK = workerK,
        bucketSize = bucketSize,
        K = k,
        pullLimit = pullLimit,
        workerParallelism = workerParallelism,
        psParallelism = psParallelism,
        iterationWaitTime = iterationWaitTime)
        
    nDCGSink.nDCGPeriodsToCsv(topK, output, 86400, false)
    
    env execute s"Online evaluation of model $model without learning"
}

%python
def plot(in_learn, in_nolearn, in_online):
    data = np.loadtxt(in_learn, delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    data2 = np.loadtxt(in_nolearn, delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    #datao = np.loadtxt(in_online, delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    dataa = pd.read_csv(in_online, delimiter=',', header=None)
    day = data[:,0]
    firstday = day[0]
    lastday = day[-1]
    datab = dataa[dataa[0] >= firstday]
    data00 = datab[datab[0] <= lastday]
    inv = data[:,1]
    nDCG = data[:,2]
    hit = data[:,3]
    day2 = data2[:,0]
    inv2 = data2[:,1]
    nDCG2 = data2[:,2]
    hit2 = data2[:,3]
    #day3 = datao[:,0]
    #inv3 = datao[:,1]
    #nDCG3 = datao[:,2]
    #hit3 = datao[:,3]
    day3 = data00[0]
    inv3 = data00[1]
    nDCG3 = data00[2]
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
    ax = fig.add_subplot(221)
    #ax2 = fig.add_subplot(222)
    
    ax.set_ylabel('nDCG')
    #ax2.set_ylabel('hit')
    
    fig.subplots_adjust(right=0.75)
    
    #ax2.set_frame_on(True)
    #ax2.patch.set_visible(False)
    
    #for i in range(0, min(len(day), len(day2))):
    #    nDCG2[i] = nDCG2[i] * inv2[i] / inv[i]
    #    hit2[i] = hit2[i] * inv2[i] / inv[i]
    
    ax.plot(day3, nDCG3, marker='o', color="Green", label="online mf")
    ax.plot(day2, nDCG2, marker='o', color="Red", label="periodic batch mf")
    ax.plot(day, nDCG, marker='o', color="Purple", label="batch then online mf")
    ax.tick_params(axis='y', colors="Black")
    
    ax.legend()
    #ax2.legend()
    ax.grid()
    #ax2.grid
    plt.ylim(0,0.04)
    plt.show()

%sh
#!/bin/sh

FILEPATH=/home/zarandy/Documents/sztaki/git/flink-ps/testoutput/ndcg.zeppelin
rm $FILEPATH.avg
rm $FILEPATH.nolearn.avg
rm $FILEPATH.online.avg
rm $FILEPATH.daily
rm $FILEPATH.nolearn.daily

for w in {19..28}
do
    cat $FILEPATH.$w >> $FILEPATH.daily
    cat $FILEPATH.nolearn.$w >> $FILEPATH.nolearn.daily
    sumInv=0
    sumnDCG=0.0
    sumHit=0
    sumInv_NoLearn=0
    sumnDCG_NoLearn=0.0
    sumHit_NoLearn=0
    sumInv_Online=0
    sumnDCG_Online=0.0
    sumHit_Online=0
    while read line
    do
    	regex=^$(echo $line | cut -d , -f 1)
		inv=$(echo $line | cut -d , -f 2)
    	sumInv=$(echo $sumInv+$inv | bc -l)	
    	sumnDCG=$(echo $(echo $line | cut -d , -f 3)*$inv+$sumnDCG | bc -l)	
    	sumHit=$(echo $(echo $line | cut -d , -f 4)*$inv+$sumHit | bc -l)	
		inv_NoLearn=$(grep "$regex" $FILEPATH.nolearn.$w | cut -d , -f 2)
    	sumInv_NoLearn=$(echo $sumInv_NoLearn+$inv_NoLearn | bc -l)	
    	sumnDCG_NoLearn=$(echo $(grep "$regex" $FILEPATH.nolearn.$w | cut -d , -f 3)*$inv_NoLearn+$sumnDCG_NoLearn | bc -l)	
    	sumHit_NoLearn=$(echo $(grep "$regex" $FILEPATH.nolearn.$w | cut -d , -f 4)*$inv_NoLearn+$sumHit_NoLearn | bc -l)	
		inv_Online=$(grep "$regex" $FILEPATH.online.all | cut -d , -f 2)
    	sumInv_Online=$(echo $sumInv_Online+$inv_Online | bc -l)	
    	sumnDCG_Online=$(echo $(grep "$regex" $FILEPATH.online.all | cut -d , -f 3)*$inv_Online+$sumnDCG_Online | bc -l)	
    	sumHit_Online=$(echo $(grep "$regex" $FILEPATH.online.all | cut -d , -f 4)*$inv_Online+$sumHit_Online | bc -l)	
	done< "$FILEPATH.$w"
    echo "$w,$sumInv,$(echo $sumnDCG/$sumInv|bc -l),$(echo $sumHit/$sumInv|bc -l)" >> $FILEPATH.avg
    echo "$w,$sumInv_NoLearn,$(echo $sumnDCG_NoLearn/$sumInv_NoLearn|bc -l),$(echo $sumHit_NoLearn/$sumInv_NoLearn|bc -l)" >> $FILEPATH.nolearn.avg
    echo "$w,$sumInv_Online,$(echo $sumnDCG_Online/$sumInv_Online|bc -l),$(echo $sumHit_Online/$sumInv_Online|bc -l)" >> $FILEPATH.online.avg
done
